Package: SAR
Title: Smart Adaptive Recommendations
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Hong", "Ooi", , "hongooi@microsoft.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Microsoft", role="cph")
    )
Description: SAR is a fast, scalable, adaptive algorithm for personalized recommendations based on user transactions and items description. It produces easily explainable/interpretable recommendations and handles "cold item" and "semi-cold user" scenarios. This package provides two implementations of SAR: a standalone implementation, and an interface to a web service in Azure. The former allows fast and easy experimentation, and the latter provides robust scalability and extra features for production use.
